import React from 'react'


import './Components.css';
import {Link} from 'react-router-dom';
import { Container,  Card } from 'react-bootstrap';


function Options() {
 
    return (
        <Container className='Options'>
       <Link to="/">  
        <Card className='ho'>
           Home
        </Card>
      </Link>
         <Link to="/assignments">
          <Card>
         Assignments
          </Card></Link>
       <Link to="/groupwork">    <Card>
         Groupwork
          </Card></Link>
        <Link to="/lessons">  <Card>
            Lessons
          </Card></Link>
         <Link to="/resources">  <Card>
           Resources
          </Card></Link>
    </Container>
    )
  }


export default Options;
